g.text: Show all
blogs
It allows us to view all the blogs
created by every user on the site.
We have an issue in terms of
keeping the cards identical size
and keeping the more info
button within the card.
The more info button allows us
to enter a new page to view
comments and to add your own
comment.
We also created a search bar to
allow users to search up specific
titles. In the future, we would like to
add a search bar to find specific
users blogs.
